Package: supervisoR
Type: Package
Title: Pathway Enrichment Visualization
Version: 0.99.0
Author: person("Hans Adam Boegh", "Marstrand-Joergensen",
  email = "adamboegh@gmail.com",
  role = c("cre","aut"),
  comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-5917-3154"))
Maintainer: Hans Adam Boegh Marstrand-Joergensen <adamboegh@gmail.com>
Description: Package enabling visualization of hierarchical pathways across many conditions.
  Currently working with REACTOME pathways, enabling exploratory data analyses of a given parent pathway and all of it's children.
  Works for an arbitrary number of groups (tested with n=20) and with arbitrary input data, though we recommend using directional enrichment scores.
  Contains both a shiny app for exploration and commands for the generation of hierarchical plots.
